snippet.title: PC Announcement | Warcraft Rumble
snippet.description:
Rumble is coming to PC! Mark your calendars for December 10, 2024 and jump into Rumble via BattleNet

Play on iOS/Android today: https://blizz.ly/3EL45BT

Follow us on social!
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/warcraftrumble
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WarcraftRumble/
Twitter: https://x.com/warcraftrumble
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/warcraftrumble

Stay up to date on all things Warcraft Rumble here: 
https://warcraftrumble.blizzard.com
